blocks.subject: NEWS: bill signed?
text: Let's just keep it at 10 so we don't have to re-coordinate things.

blocks.subject: RE: Thursday
text: I'm back.  I just changed my hair appt. to next week.  Would you rather meet
at 9 or 9:30 in the a.m.?  Let me know soon so I can change everyone around.
Should we leave it?  Phyllis is o.k. with either time.

blocks.subject: RE: Thursday    Please call Carol.  How about the Buffalo Grille, or is that too busy?                        "Patti Young"                                                  RE: Thursday                                           PM
raw_header: Please call Carol.  How about the Buffalo Grille, or is that too busy?
text: Good!!  If you want to get Hollie, Lucinda, etc., to come, please feel free
to do so.  Is there any special place you want to go???
I have been thinking about you as well.  I have your bicycle and will
return
it to you when you are ready for it.  I can bring it on Saturday.  Will it
fit in your car?  If not, I can drop it by after breakfast.  Might need to
come by anyway to see what else you have done to it.
I will call Carol, too, if you don't care.

blocks.subject: Re: Thursday
text: Breakfast at 10:00 sounds great!  Wherever you want to go...also, I need to
get my bike back from you, I might be doing some biking.  I've been
thinking about you.  Hope all is going well.
"Patti Young"

blocks.subject: Thursday                                           PM
text: Miss Tana,
Is there a chance you might like to try to get together this weekend?  I
thought I would check with you first and then see if Phyllis is available.
I have a hair appointment at 8 a.m. on Saturday.  We could do breakfast at
10, or whatever...
Let me know.
Patti
